            <div id="kmrb-overview" class="project-overview">
                <h3 class="overview-name">project overview —</h3>
                <p class="overview">Komorebi Lemon Mochi (木漏れ日レモンもち) is a brand of packaged Japanese mochi rice cakes.
                    The brand target audience is adults from pages 22 and up, including parents with children, people
                    who are interested in traditional Japanese products. gift givers and collectors. This project
                    provides Komorebi with a brand system and a package prototype for product distribution. </p>
            </div>
            <div id="kmrb-goals" class="project-goals">
                <h3 class="goals-name">goals —</h3>
                <p class="goals">Komorebi’s package design mission is to create an environmentally-friendly and engaging
                    experience for its customers. Aiming to be on the higher end of similar products price list and
                    specifically target sophisticated adults instead of the usual children-marketed like its
                    competitors, Komorebi knock-down package design tells a story as the customer opens the product.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
